<p>
<lb n="1"/>vikāri saṁvatsa 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ra puṣya ba lu ya 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rrābhaṭlu mallubha 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭlu taṁbaḷa jakkaya 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ku rāsi yiccina yadu 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rugaḍa nīyavasara ni 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>mityaṁ mācātanu Apu 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>gā puccukoṁnā rokhaṁ 
<lb n="9"/>ga ṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> māḍānu yidinā 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>nu nāku celliṁstiri ganka 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>nu cellenuni peṭṭina patra 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṁ pōyagankanu Āpa 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>traṁ yakkaḍaganka vuṁ 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>nānu caccupatraṁ <unclear>vi</unclear> 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ḷitapatraṁ yiṁddulku 
<lb n="16"/>sākṣi yīśvaruḍu vī 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>rabhadruṁḍu śrī śrī jē 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>yunu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

